      For more information, please fill the following form and we will get
      back to you shortly.</p>

    <div class="dropdown email-dropdown">Subject <span class="about-caret caret"></span>
      <ul class="email-menu dropdown-menu">
        <li class="subject-item">Rental Inquiry</li>
        <li class="subject-item">Sales</li>
        <li class="subject-item">Career Opportunities</li>
        <li class="subject-item">Other</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <p class="about-email about-email-title">Message</p>
    <form class="about-email" action="//formspree.io/lionshareinc@gmail.com" method="POST">
      <input class="about-subject" type="hidden" name="_subject" value="No subject" />
      <input class="return-email about-form"
             type="email"
             name="_replyto"
             placeholder="Your email address">
      <textarea class="email-message about-form"
                name="message"
